✅ How to Use This Plan
Every day:
1.	Understand the problem pattern
2.	Write a recursive solution
3.	Add memoization
4.	Convert to tabulation
5.	(Optional) Do space optimization
________________________________________
🔰 WEEK 1: DP BASICS + 1D DP FOUNDATION
